{"type": "article", "id": 29771, "title": "竹制咖啡桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-18T22:47:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160718201118DpWxwg2LVsq7Q3lZ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>第一眼看到这款名为 LOCK 的咖啡桌时，你或许很难想象用来支撑它的扭曲的桌腿实际上是由竹子制成的。这种和木材相比更加环保的材料已经成为不少设计师用来探索更多造型可能时的首选，荷兰设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.planktonstation.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Plankton Station</a> 将竹子切片之后拼接在一起，通过相扣的结构来保证整张桌子的稳定性。为了更好地搭配咖啡桌的概念，部分的竹片被染上了焦糖色，其余则不做颜色处理，层层叠叠的造型就像是拉花一样，富有新意。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/lock-bamboo-coffee-table-plankton-07-15-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1386 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718201132oPsNBLMfJuKg813h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695599\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718201132cf1VkwOGybHtoD43.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680929\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718201132EwjHNLzu7hQmbF9B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718201132IEJWfU2tZvk4MegQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.723716\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}